                        <interp inst="t18390513-name-999" type="given" value="HENRY MASTERMAN"></interp>HENRY MASTERMAN MARSHALL</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a commander in the Navy, and live at Limehouse. I expected 24lbs. of candles, which I had ordered of Mr. Robinson, in King William-street—I did not receive them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390513-name-1000" type="witnessName">
