                        <interp inst="t18390513-name-1000" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH CROSLEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am an inmate of the Destitute Sailors' Asylum. On the 18th of April I gave the prisoner the candles to take to Captain Marshall's house.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> He told me to take them to the turnpike, and wait there till he came. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> No, I told him to take them to Captain Marshall, as I had other places to go to.</p>
               <p>
